== 發行 ==
2014年12月，墨菲和羅伯森的首張劇照釋出<ref name="DEADLINE">{{cite web|url=http://deadline.com/2014/12/eddie-murphy-britt-robertson-cook-movie-photo-1201309107/|title=Eddie Murphy Shows His Dramatic Side In ‘Cook’ – First Look Photo|website=[[Deadline.com|Deadline.com]]|first=Denise|last=Petski|date=2014-12-04|accessdate=2016-04-21|archive-date=2016-04-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160426130149/http://deadline.com/2014/12/eddie-murphy-britt-robertson-cook-movie-photo-1201309107/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。電影最先於2016年4月22日在[[翠貝卡影展|翠貝卡影展]]上作全球首映<ref name="TRIBECA"/>。[[華納兄弟影業|華納兄弟影業]]也作為國際市場上的發行公司之一，而美國本地則由[[Cinelou_Films|Cinelou Films]]的Cinelou Releasing負責發行<ref name="DEADLINE"/><ref>{{cite web|url=http://blogs.indiewire.com/shadowandact/first-clip-poster-for-eddie-murphys-first-film-in-five-years-mr-church-20160423|title=First Clip + Poster for Eddie Murphy's First Film in Five Years - 'Mr. Church'|website=[[Indiewire.com|Indiewire.com]]|first=Tambay|last=A. Obenson|date=2016-04-23|accessdate=2016-04-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160424115949/http://blogs.indiewire.com/shadowandact/first-clip-poster-for-eddie-murphys-first-film-in-five-years-mr-church-20160423|archive-date=2016-04-24|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。美國於2016年9月16日上映<ref>{{cite web|url=http://variety.com/2016/film/news/eddie-murphy-britt-robertson-drama-mr-church-release-1201825912/|title=Eddie Murphy Drama ‘Mr. Church’ Gets September Release|website=[[Variety_(magazine)|Variety]]|first=Dave|last=McNary|date=2016-07-28|accessdate=2016-07-28|archive-date=2016-07-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160729153058/http://variety.com/2016/film/news/eddie-murphy-britt-robertson-drama-mr-church-release-1201825912/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

